

### Google Chrome standalone offline installer, links for 32 bit and 64 versions.

Google Chrome 32-bit (x86):

<a href='http://www.google.com/chrome/eula.html?standalone=1'> 32-bit Google Chrome Offline Installer </a>  (Single user account, 40MB)

<http://www.google.com/chrome/eula.html?system=true&standalone=1'> 32-bit Google Chrome Offline Installer </a> (All user accounts, 40MB)

Google Chrome 64-bit (x64):

<a href='http://www.google.com/chrome/eula.html?standalone=1&platform=win64'> 64-bit Google Chrome Offline Installer </a>  (Single user account, 46MB)

<a href='http://www.google.com/chrome/eula.html?system=true&standalone=1&platform=win64'> 64-bit Google Chrome Offline Installer </a> (All user accounts, 46MB)

